Legal Technology Company, LawPavilion Business Solutions Limited has pledged to help lawyers cope with the COVID-19 pandemic by providing Electronic Law Reports to young lawyers. 
   
This it said, followed its partnership with the leadership of the Nigerian Bar Association (NBA), led by Mr. Paul Usoro (SAN). 
   
Ope Olugasa, the Managing Director of the company also commended Usoro and his executives for the well thought out initiative of giving back to the legal community, particularly the young lawyers.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .